xcode:set-default-configuration

Full name:

com.sap.prd.mobile.ios.mios:xcode-maven-plugin:1.2.1-SNAPSHOT:set-default-configuration

Description:

Sets default values needed during Xcode build.

Attributes:

  • Requires a Maven project to be executed.

Required Parameters

Name Type Since Description
project MavenProject - (no description)

Parameter Details

(no description)

  • Required: Yes
  • Expression: ${project}
